rComments: Steve is a really good teacher with good qualities. He's very interested in what he talks about and makes it fun for everyone. Although the tests are difficult, it has nothing to do with Steve since he's not the one writing the tests.
He's definitely good. Watch out though, he might be conditioning you.
He is funny and his class is super interesting!!! I love his class so much. You should take his class if you are going to PSYC 100.
Best instructor I've EVER had!  Really knows his stuff.  Class is never dull with him!  Sweet guy!

Amazing TA.  His lectures were always interesting and he kept the class interested with jokes.  Sometimes played fun video clips.  Also, the quizzes were online which was not like that for all sections.
Easy class if you go. Not a blow-off though. This guy's good at his craft, on of the best TA's I've had at Illinois
